The Municipal Treasurer should also not allow the issuance of new Accountable forms to Collectors and/or Liquidating Officers without the Reports of Collections and Deposit and validated deposit slips, in case the latter is authorized by her. The Municipal Treasurer should impose stricter internal controls in the establishing accountabilities of all the collecting officers.

